reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pretty decent palette for the price
reviews.reviewText: This is a pretty good palette for beginners. It's got a variety of shades. I like how it comes with multiple mattes, shimmers/metallics and even comes with blush, contour and highlight shades (although I feel it's important to know that the contour shades would really only fit light to light-medium skin tones). There were also a few shades that were too close in color. Another thing to keep in mind would be that some shades (specifically the mattes) will stain your skin a little.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A lot of value for your dollar
reviews.reviewText: The packaging is great with this product. It is big but yet it is small. You get a large variety of eye colors in a package that is small in size when it is closed. You can take this on trips or vacations. It comes with a variety of brushes so you can choose which one you prefer . The images that are shown are exactly what you get. I think it is a good value.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars An absolute bargain!
reviews.reviewText: This palette is absolutely beautiful 😍 the outside is silver and the inside is gold and glittery. I swatched some of the colors like the glitters, highlighter,brown contour,and a few of the dark colors bc usually in cheaper palettes those aren't very pigmented. The glitters was glistening and how do I say . They were very vibrant. The highlighter was very bright and shiny as well. The dark countour and colors were very pigmented. The brushes came all wrapped separately. This kit is amazing. Would definitely recommend. There is a wide variety of colors for whatever the vibe may be. I am in love and shook.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Fun and affordable!! Wears all day with no creasing. My only gripe is there is a liiitle fall out (no big deal) and there are no fluffy blending brushes or blush brush (again, no biggie). Nice range of colors!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pigments are good
reviews.reviewText: The brushes are poor quality and pretty much useless. The eyeshades are awesome! Very good pigmentation and stays well. Not any issues with powder falling off brush on my face during application. Very happy with purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Beautifully colorful. The only thing is the reds are very pigmented so it sometimes leaves behind a little red residue, but other than that I love it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Way better than I expected.
reviews.reviewText: Great variety, nice pigmentation! Would definitely purchase again. Blends well, lasting wear.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very pigmented and a variety of eyeshadow to choose from
reviews.reviewText: My daughter loves all the different colors and is very happy with this pallette.
Dady, can I put on some makeup? Yes...Makeup will not be complex to remove from the bathtub, toilet and the wall behind the bathroom door.strongly advise to buy it in combo with magic sponge.
I have been using this pallet for almost a year now and it never disappoints! Has every color that I need and more. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewerName: I loves this and it has alot of pigment
